Program: Discovery
Title: China - the scientific revolution
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryx1
Last Broadcast Date: 08 March 2005
How China is once again establishing itself as a pioneering scientific force. For centuries, China was the leading light in science. Scholars led the way in fields as diverse as engineering and astronomy. Geoff Watts finds out how the country is once again establishing itself as a dominant force in the world of science. Show less